                <td colspan="2" valign="top"><div align="center"><B><FONT face="Monotype Corosiva" size=4>SCHEME FOR COMPASSIONATE APPOINTMENT</FONT></B></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td colspan="2" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td></td>
                <td colspan="2" valign="top"><font color="#008000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" class="textsmall style36">The MPR Division runs a scheme for compassionate appointment. </font><FONT size=1 face=Verdana class="textsmall">The object of the Scheme is to grant appointment on compassionate grounds to adependent family member of a Government servant dying in harness or who is retired on medical grounds, thereby leaving his family in penury and without any means of livelihood, to relieve the family of the Government servant concerned from financial destitution and to help it get over the emergency.</FONT></td>
